name: The Dance of Ultimate Trust
description:
Something is behind my eyes. Frames per second, flittering. A dream that moves and I feel my body free from all anxiety. Full trust is the future ahead and the people I surround myself. A dance of trust. Abstraction and form. 

Made with hydra code, vintage mixers, and video feedback. 

Music by Nyhos, a sound project I was in from 2011-2016.
